@startuml
!theme plain
title Arsitektur Sistem Tempat Sampah Otomatis (Standalone)

package "Perangkat Keras (Hardware)" {
    [Sensor Infrared] as Sensor
    [Motor Servo] as Servo
    [Mikrokontroler\n(ESP32/Arduino)] as MCU
    [Sumber Daya\n(Baterai/Adaptor)] as Power
}

package "Lingkungan Fisik" {
    [Pengguna / Tangan] as User
}

' Alur
Power --> MCU : Suplai Listrik
User --> Sensor : Gerakan Terdeteksi (Ada objek)
Sensor --> MCU : Kirim Sinyal Digital (LOW/HIGH)
MCU --> Servo : Kirim Sinyal PWM (Perintah Buka)

note bottom of MCU
  Memproses logika:
  Jika ada gerakan -> Buka
  Tunggu 3-5 detik -> Tutup
end note

note right of Servo
  Mengerakkan Tuas
  Tutup Sampah
end note

@enduml